<quantity box="[769,856,151,177]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.2" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" unit="mm" value="4.2">4.2 mm</quantity>
. Equal to the 
<typeStatus box="[1014,1112,151,177]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">holotype</typeStatus>
except in the pronotal punctures finer and sparser and pygidial apex rounder. Female 
<typeStatus box="[794,906,187,213]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">paratypes</typeStatus>
: length: 7.8–8.0 mm; width: 
<quantity box="[1224,1358,187,213]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.75" metricValueMax="3.9" metricValueMin="3.6" pageId="49" pageNumber="50" unit="mm" value="3.75" valueMax="3.9" valueMin="3.6">3.6–3.9 mm</quantity>
. Equal to the 
<typeStatus box="[221,319,223,249]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">holotype</typeStatus>
except in the abdomen with bristles less abundant and more sparse.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="49" pageNumber="50" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="49.[151,1437,150,682]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,328,259,285]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Etymology</emphasis>
